==English==

===Proverb===
'''[[too many]] [[cook]]s [[spoil]] [[the]] [[broth]]'''

# If too many people work at a task, the end product could be ruined.

===See also===
*[[the more the merrier]]

====Translations====
*German: (zu) [[Viele Köche verderben den Brei]]
*Japanese: [[船頭多くして船山に登る]]
*Russian: [[У семи нянек дитя без глазу]]
*Swedish: [[Ju fler kockar, desto sämre soppa]]
*Finnish: [[Mitä useampi kokki, sitä huonompi soppa]]
*Greek: [[Όπου λαλούν πολλοί κοκκόροι αργεί να ξημερώσει]] (Where many cocks cry dawn is late)
